reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Adds a nice touch to the bedroom and provides the perfect amount of light as a bedside lamp. Not over powering but enough for what is necessary without needing the overhead. Perfect size for our smaller side tables too, and I love that it has USB ports and a regular block port. Pull chain is more convenient than reaching up inside for a switch. Highly recommend. The grey color goes so well with our room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These were perfect for what I needed. Ordered the grey shades, as the white seemed too bright for the bedroom. Perfect lamp shade color. I prefer a pull chain as opposed to a touch light, seem to last longer. Added feature of two charging ports, and another plug option. Packaging strong and thoughtful for these lamps. Great buy!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Loves these lamos
reviews.reviewText: These lamps were easy and cheap to set up, make my room feel every modern. Love that they have usb ports and also a plug makes it easier to charged phones and etc! They have lasted as well with no problems

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good price, nice ambience for a bedroom, the built in plug/usb is handy!
reviews.reviewText: Needed some simple nightstand lamps with a small footprint for guest room. These are very minimalistic in appearance, they don't overpower the room. It gives off is a soft, bedroom appropriate light that creates a warm and comfortable ambience if you use a warm led bulb, which we did. It would be just as easy to use a bright led bulb if brighter lighting is your thing. The lamp is pretty heavy, not easily pulled around on the nightstand. I prefer the convenience of touch control, but for the price the pull chain is easy enough to find and use, even in the dark. They look like decent quality, no one would think you spent hundreds on them, but no one would think they were super cheap looking either. Good value, especially since they come in a matched set of 2!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love these lamps
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Better than I expected. These lamps are the perfect size for a night stand or desktopThat are very sleek and sturdy. The USB port works perfect to keep my phone and beats charging at my desk while I'm working and keeps everything in hands reach. I'm glad I made the purchase.
